ssues. :)</span><hr size=1> I met up with a lev 14 cleric in game a while back. He's a nice hunting partner, so I find myself teaming up with him quite often. Now, myself would be a now proud level 12 ranger. I got.. helped a bit by a nice person from this guild in the beginning of this char, so I have this spiffy gear and this reasonable level, but I'm not bothered by any form of intelligence when it comes to gameplay.<br>
<br>
