<br>
A wee goblin camp! It's so cute! And all these cute little goblin thingies! Awww!! I just can't stop peering at them. Not even when one of them comes a bit closer, still unaware of me, as if to say &quot;Hey you.. Get lost!&quot;.. Still, I can't stop looking.<br>
<br>
